---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout>
  <h1>Fit-Check</h1>
<h2>Before you apply</h2>
<p>This is a 15-minute diagnostic conversation. It is not a coaching session, strategy call, or full audit. The purpose is to determine whether there is a fit and identify the most appropriate course of action.</p>

<p>I’m going to confirm the pattern, assess whether this is the right kind of work, and then tell you the best next step: paid Audit for program application, waitlist, resource, or referral.</p>


<blockquote>
  <strong>Fit-Check Fee:</strong> USD 0 <br> 
  <strong>No-show / late cancellation fee:</strong>USD 50

  <br>
  Cancellations or rescheduling must be made at least **48 hours before** the scheduled call. If you do not attend, or cancel/reschedule within 48 hours, you authorize a USD 50 charge.
</blockquote>


  <form
  action="https://buttondown.com/api/emails/embed-subscribe/fit-check-with-cyrus"
  method="post"
  class="embeddable-buttondown-form"
>
    <label for="recent_freeze"
      >In 1–3 sentences, describe your most recent freeze.</label
    >
    <blockquote>
      Freeze means the moment pressure hit and you lost access to clean action.
      This may look like silence, shutdown, delay, avoidance, appeasement,
      overthinking, emotional absence, or not saying what needed to be said.
    </blockquote>

    <textarea
      name="metadata__recent_freeze"
      id="recent_freeze"
      rows="5"
      cols="33"
      required></textarea>

    <fieldset>
      <legend>What area is this affecting most?</legend>

      <div>
        <input
          type="radio"
          name="metadata__area_affected"
          id="marriage_relationship"
          value="marriage_relationship"
          required
        />
        <label for="marriage_relationship">Marriage / Relationship</label>
      </div>

      <div>
        <input
          type="radio"
          name="metadata__area_affected"
          id="fatherhood"
          value="fatherhood"
          required
        />
        <label for="fatherhood">Fatherhood</label>
      </div>

      <div>
        <input
          type="radio"
          name="metadata__area_affected"
          id="work_mission"
          value="work_mission"
          required
        />
        <label for="work_mission">Work / Mission</label>
      </div>

      <div>
        <input
          type="radio"
          name="metadata__area_affected"
          id="discipline"
          value="discipline"
          required
        />
        <label for="discipline">Discipline</label>
      </div>

      <div>
        <input
          type="radio"
          name="metadata__area_affected"
          id="confidence"
          value="confidence"
          required
        />
        <label for="confidence">Confidence</label>
      </div>

      <div>
        <input
          type="radio"
          name="metadata__area_affected"
          id="decision_making"
          value="decision_making"
          required
        />
        <label for="decision_making">Decision-Making</label>
      </div>

      <div>
        <input
          type="radio"
          name="metadata__area_affected"
          id="other"
          value="other"
          required
        />
        <label for="other">Other</label>
      </div>
    </fieldset>

    <legend>Confirmations</legend>

    <div>
      <input
        type="checkbox"
        id="confirmation_call"
        name="metadata__confirmation_call"
        required
      />
      <label for="confirmation_call"
        >I understand this is a 15-minute Fit-Check, not a coaching session or
        full audit. The purpose is to confirm fit and identify the right next
        step.</label
      >
    </div>

    <div>
      <input
        type="checkbox"
        id="confirmation_fee"
        name="metadata__confirmation_fee"
        required
      />
      <label for="confirmation_fee"
        >I understand the Fit-Check is USD 0 to book. If I do not attend, or if
        I cancel/reschedule less than 48 hours before the call, I authorize a
        USD 50 no-show / late cancellation charge.</label
      >
    </div>

    <fieldset>
      <legend>Contact Details</legend>

      <label for="first_name">First Name</label>
      <input type="text" name="metadata__first_name" id="first_name" required />

      <label for="last_name">Last Name</label>
      <input type="text" name="metadata__last_name" id="last_name" required />

      <label for="bd-email">Enter your email</label>
      <input type="email" name="email" id="bd-email" required />
    </fieldset>

    <input type="submit" value="Send The Booking Link" />
  </form>
</BaseLayout>
